│ Replace the line:                                                                          │
│ ```cpp                                                                                     │
│ clearDependencies();                                                                       │
│ ```                                                                                        │
│ with:                                                                                      │
│ ```cpp                                                                                     │
│ initDependencies();                                                                        │
│ ```                                                                                        │
│                                                                                            │
│ This ensures that the `Dependencies` field is initialized to `0` when the `init` method is │
│ called.                                                                                    │
